You will be part of a team that coordinates, reviews and manages civil engineering projects such as geotechnical and structural engineering works. &nbsp;You will need to carry out technical reviews and analysis for new and existing HDB properties, and conduct audits at project sites. &nbsp;Your work may also involve preparing cost estimates and project schedules, procurement of technical services and project management. You should possess a good degree in Civil Engineering recognised by the Professional Engineers Board of Singapore. Those with knowledge of the relevant engineering design software or Building Information Modelling software, and working experience in geotechnical or structural engineering projects will be an asset.



Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.
